<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an König Rupprecht I. </head><p>Der Rat übersendet Abschriften von Fehdebriefen, die am Matthiastag zugegangen sind, und bittet für sich und andere Reichsstädte um Schutz.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_19" id="8r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_19_r2l2">Kunig</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_19_r2l5"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_r2l3">furſt vnd </ab></add> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns ſind etlıch entſagſbrief 
<del rend="strikethrough">kumen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_r2l4">geſant </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l7">vnd erſt nü an ſant Matheis abent 
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_r2l6">des <expan>ʒwelfpot<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> nehſt vergangen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l8"><expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> worden / der wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> abſchrift <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l10">hyrynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gnade </del> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l12">mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒe / daʒ Jr von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1570701902931_666"><expan>furſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> etwaʒ darcʒu tun </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_19_line_1570701907648_671">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gedenck<ex>en</ex></expan> w</del></ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l13">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd beſtellen wöllet / daʒ </del> darcʒu <expan>gedencke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd tun wollet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l14">daʒ wir vnd <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> des Reichs Stete darunter icht ʒe - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_19_r2l15">ſchaden <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> / Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_19" id="8r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Kunig </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>furst und</add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns sind etlich entsagsbrief
                        <add>gesant</add> und erst nü an <app><note><q type="date">sant Matheis abent, <add>des
                                    <expan>zwelfpot<ex>en</ex></expan></add> nehst vergangen
                        </q>25.02.1408</note></app>, <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> worden, der wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> abschrift
                            <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan>, hyrynne
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slosse<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                            <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisze, daz ir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>furstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> darczu <expan>gedencke<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        tun wollet, daz wir und <expan>ande<ex>r</ex></expan> des reichs stete
                        darunter icht zeschaden <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das wöllen
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
